title: Sierra Leone Consumer Price Index Cpi
description: Consumer Price Index CPI in Sierra Leone increased to 125.20 points in September from 122.79 points in August of 2022. Consumer Price Index CPI in Sierra Leone averaged 156.86 points from 2007 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 318.20 points in September of 2020 and a record low of 86.89 points in January of 2021. This page provides - Sierra Leone Consumer Price Index Cpi- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics Sierra Leone
